\title{Every adjunction restricts to an equivalence}
\taxon{proposition}
\import{macros}

\p{If we restrict the functors of an [adjunction](math-0028) to the fixpoints of #{FG} and #{GF}, the adjoint functors form an [equivalence of categories](math-002B).}
